    "PRIMARY faithfulness gate (BINDING for all fields): JAX fp64 vs the fp64 WRF oracle. All 6 regimes match to ~1e-13 relative on every field (theta, qv, qc, qr, qi, qs, qg, Ni, Ns, Nr, Ng) and surface precip -- a faithful transcription of the scheme, not a self-compare.",
